{"an7.10:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 7.10 ","an7.10:0.2":"1. Dhanavagga ","an7.10:0.3":"Macchariyasutta ","an7.10:1.1":"“Sattimani, bhikkhave, samyojanani. ","an7.10:1.2":"Katamani satta? ","an7.10:1.3":"Anunayasamyojanam, patighasamyojanam, ditthisamyojanam, vicikicchasamyojanam, manasamyojanam, issasamyojanam, macchariyasamyojanam. ","an7.10:1.4":"Imani kho, bhikkhave, satta samyojanani”ti. ","an7.10:1.5":"Dasamam. ","an7.10:1.6":"Dhanavaggo pathamo. ","an7.10:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","an7.10:2.1":"Dve piyani balam dhanam, ","an7.10:2.2":"Sankhittanceva vitthatam; ","an7.10:2.3":"Uggam samyojananceva, ","an7.10:2.4":"Pahanam macchariyena cati. "}